................. more about being a computer programmer.","options":["across","up","off","out"],"correctAnswer":"out","questionType":"VOCAB","audioUrl":""},{"id":256,"mongoQuestionId":"69c8f2f51f0f44d8052a2991","questionText":"The baby can\'t walk down the ........ alone. Help him.","options":["staircase","wardrobes","garage"],"correctAnswer":"staircase","questionType":"VOCAB","audioUrl":""},{"id":176,"mongoQuestionId":"69c8f2f21f0f44d8052a2941","questionText":"I don\'t know much about computers, so I asked the assistant for ............................ advice.","options":["a lot","many","a few","a little"],"correctAnswer":"a little","questionType":"VOCAB","audioUrl":""},{"id":164,"mongoQuestionId":"69c8f2f11f0f44d8052a2935","questionText":"............................ never played this game before.","options":["I\'ve","I"],"correctAnswer":"I\'ve","questionType":"VOCAB","audioUrl":""},{"id":170,"mongoQuestionId":"69c8f2f11f0f44d8052a293b","questionText":"‘We\'re moving house tomorrow.’ ‘Really? ............................ you with the furniture.’","options":["I help","I\'m helping","I\'ll help"],"correctAnswer":"I\'ll help","questionType":"VOCAB","audioUrl":""},{"id":252,"mongoQuestionId":"69c8f2f51f0f44d8052a298d","questionText":"The gardener decided to retire ......... the age of fifty.","options":["in","with","at","of"],"correctAnswer":"at","questionType":"VOCAB","audioUrl":""},{"id":173,"mongoQuestionId":"69c8f2f11f0f44d8052a293e","questionText":"My mum ............................ the bus to work every morning, but Dad drives.","options":["catches","does","runs","goes"],"correctAnswer":"catches","questionType":"VOCAB","audioUrl":""}]},{"nodeId":7,"title":"Listening","nodeType":"LISTENING","questions":[{"id":2784,"mongoQuestionId":"69c8f42e1f0f44d8052a33a9","questionText":"Help us to help the environment!\\\\nDonate: old computer equipment mobile _______(1)\\\\nWe _______(2) them to raise funds for homeless _______(3)\\\\nDrop-off point: 705, Milner _______(4)